name: __ERigVMRegisterType
doc: The type of register within the memory.

String: bool, int32, float, FVector etc. (also structs that do NOT require a constructor / destructor to be valid)
Name: ERigVMRegisterType
FString
Invalid: Any USTRUCT (structs which require a constructor / destructor to be valid. structs which have indirection (arrays or strings in them, for example).
